getTransactionCount(bool,bool).return: Total number of transactions after filters are applied.

params.from: Index start position of transaction array.
params.to: Index end position of transaction array.

params.owner: Address of owner to be replaced.

devdoc.title: Multisignature wallet - Allows multiple parties to agree on  transactions before execution.

addOwner(address).notice: Allows to add a new owner. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.

changeRequirement(uint256).notice: Allows to change the number of required confirmations. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.

confirmTransaction(uint256).notice: Allows an owner to confirm a transaction.

methods.constructor: Contract constructor sets initial owners and required number  of confirmations.

executeTransaction(uint256).notice: Allows anyone to execute a confirmed transaction.

getConfirmationCount(uint256).notice: Get the number of confirmations of a transaction.

getConfirmations(uint256).notice: Get the array with owner addresses, which confirmed transaction.

getTransactionCount(bool,bool).notice: Get the total number of transactions after filers are applied.

getTransactionIds(uint256,uint256,bool,b.notice: Get the list of transaction IDs in defined range.

isConfirmed(uint256).notice: Returns the confirmation status of a transaction.

removeOwner(address).notice: Allows to remove an owner. Transaction has to be sent by wallet.

replaceOwner(address,address).notice: Allows to replace an owner with a new owner. Transaction has  to be sent by wallet.

revokeConfirmation(uint256).notice: Allows an owner to revoke a confirmation for a transaction.

submitTransaction(address,uint256,bytes).notice: Allows an owner to submit and confirm a transaction.
